pulses.name: 20240829 Most Active Threat Indicators
pulses.description:
29 Aug 2024 : Most Active Threat Indicators
#Cybersecurity #Cyberattack #RCE #Botnet #IOC

Top 3 Source Countries:

- China (CN): Responsible for multiple attacks exploiting vulnerabilities in NETGEAR and D-Link devices, as well as the Mozi botnet.
- India (IN): Involved in attacks targeting NETGEAR devices, the Mozi botnet, and GPON routers, as well as a DDWRT HTTP Daemon vulnerability.
- Mexico (MX): Observed in attacks related to the Mozi botnet.
